<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Firstlink Exim - Resend Verification Email</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f3f3f320;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 100%;
        margin: 20px auto;
      }

      .logo {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding-inline: 1rem;
      }

      .card {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #fff;
        border: 1px solid #99999960;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .title {
        line-height: 2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-align: center;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #444;
      }

      .name {
        color: black;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .btn {
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 36px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        border: none;
        background-color: #ff5252;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        cursor: pointer;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="title">
          <h2>Resend Verification Email</h2>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-top: 16px">
          Hello <span class="name"><%= name %></span>,
        </p>

        <p style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px">
          We noticed that you haven't verified your email yet. Please complete
          the verification process to activate your account.
        </p>

        <p style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 26px">
          You're just a step away from accessing all the features of our
          platform. Click the button below to verify your email address. This
          link will expire in
          <span style="color: black; font-weight: 600">10 minutes</span>.
        </p>

        <div
          style="
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            width: 100%;
          "
        >
          <a
            href="<%= href %>"
            target="_blank"
            class="btn"
            style="color: white"
          >
            Verify Email
          </a>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
          <p>Regards</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 500;">
            FirstLink Export & Import Team
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
